        p.workDescription
          | <i>Design What?</i> is a thesis publication aimed at demonstrating a
          | focused approach to information, aesthetics and audience. The goal of this project was to create a Graphic Design instruction manual
          | that both an experienced designer, or a curious patron could understand easily in addition to learn valuable information and implementation.
